data.description: Amazing one of a kind views of Hoquiam, Westport, Ocean Shores, the Bay & Hoquiam River!  3 bed, 2-1/4 bath home with a beautifully updated kitchen opening to the great room with stunning views & fireplace. Basement has spacious family room, bonus room, fireplace, half bath & laundry. Includes 2nd parcel to the NW. The deck offers entertainment space and relaxation with more breathtaking views. Patio, large yard, fire pit area, and more. Deep 2 car garage includes storage. Plenty of room for RV parking.
